## Node name — use short name with actual hostname for cluster capability
## For production: override with ERL_NODE_NAME env var or change this line
-sname erlkoenig_elf

## Cookie — set via RELX_COOKIE env var (from cookie file)
-setcookie ${RELX_COOKIE}

## Standard epmd — hardened via ERL_EPMD_ADDRESS in systemd unit
## Do NOT set -start_epmd false

## Scheduler
+sbwt very_short
